# Supabase — https://supabase.com/dashboard → your project → Connect / Project Settings → API
# 1. Project URL → NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL
# 2. Use ONE of the following (Connect modal uses publishable; older docs use anon JWT):
#    - NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY (sb_publishable_...)
#    - NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY (eyJ... legacy JWT)

NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project-ref.supabase.co
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=your-publishable-key-here
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key-here
